# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CVE-2026-4539 — Pygments <= 2.19.2
# Severity: MEDIUM (ReDoS in AdlLexer — archetype definition language)
# Affected: pygments/lexers/archetype.py
# Risk: LOCAL access only. Attacker must supply crafted .adl input to the
#        AdlLexer. This project does not process user-supplied Pygments input;
#        pygments is a transitive dev dependency of pytest, rich, and ipython.
# Mitigation: Not exposed in production (dev-only dependency). No fix version
#             available — upstream has not responded to the disclosure.
# Review date: 2026-04-28 (re-evaluate monthly for upstream fix)
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
CVE-2026-4539
